### Crear centro de costo raíz
POST {{base}}/api/cost-centers
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "CC-001",
  "name": "Urgencias",
  "parentId": null,
  "description": "Centro de costo del servicio de urgencias"
}

###

### Crear centro de costo hijo
POST {{base}}/api/cost-centers
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "CC-001-01",
  "name": "Urgencias Adultos",
  "parentId": 1,
  "description": "Sub-centro de urgencias adultos"
}

###

### Obtener por ID
GET {{base}}/api/cost-centers/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Listar con paginación
POST {{base}}/api/cost-centers/list
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 0,
  "rows": 10,
  "search": "",
  "order_by": "cc.nombre",
  "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Actualizar
PUT {{base}}/api/cost-centers/1
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Urgencias Generales",
  "parentId": null,
  "description": "Descripción actualizada"
}

###

### Activar/Inactivar
PATCH {{base}}/api/cost-centers/1/toggle-active
Authorization: {{token}}
